00:23:41,736 --> 00:23:43,321
Ini wasiatku, Kim Seung-bok.

253
00:23:43,404 --> 00:23:44,739
Kau boleh ambil griya tawangku.

254
00:23:44,822 --> 00:23:46,115
Apa kau sudah gila?

