694
00:59:45,474 --> 00:59:46,642
"Menyesal"?

695
00:59:47,810 --> 00:59:49,020
Apakah aku menyesal?

696
00:59:54,233 --> 00:59:55,234
Benar.

697
00:59:56,527 --> 00:59:57,903
Setelah hari itu,

698
00:59:59,739 --> 01:00:02,533
