01:01:46,887 --> 01:01:50,933
<font color="#00ff40"><i>RAMYEON</i> KIMCI</font>

707
01:02:27,887 --> 01:02:29,889
<i>Harusnya aku tak begitu padanya.</i>

708
01:02:30,681 --> 01:02:32,725
<i>Harusnya aku tak mengusirnya.</i>

709
01:02:33,684 --> 01:02:37,271
<i>Harusnya aku
