710
01:02:37,354 --> 01:02:38,898
<i>Harusnya aku langsung telepon dia.</i>

711
01:02:40,274 --> 01:02:41,901
<i>Harusnya aku berkata,</i>

712
01:02:42,902 --> 01:02:45,404
"Dia kakakku,"
