725
01:03:30,574 --> 01:03:32,701
Aku merindukannya setengah mati.

726
01:03:34,078 --> 01:03:35,788
Lalu kau mau aku lakukan apa?

727
01:03:36,497 --> 01:03:37,623
Kau ingin aku mengatasi

728
01:03:38,165 --> 01:03:39,416
semua perasaan itu?

729
01:03:40,000 --> 01:03:41,293
Itu gampang dikatakan.

730
01:03:41,961 --> 01:03:43,545
Namun, bagaimana bisa?

731
01:03:45,714 --> 01:03:47,341
Karena itu,

732
01:03:48,884 --> 01:03:52,680
tolong berikan saja aku obat.
Aku mohon, Seo-jin.

733
01:03:53,889 --> 01:03:55,599
Aku rasanya hampir mati.

734
01:04:16,161 --> 01:04:17,997
<i>Halo, pelanggan yang kami cintai.</i>

735
01:04:18,080 --> 01:04:22,126
<i>Aku Lee Eun-ji, tim pelayanan pelanggan
Quantum & Time.</i>

736
01:04:22,209 --> 01:04:23,544
